{"word":"προχειρίζω","slug":"προχειρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προχειρίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> attic <el>ιῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to put into the hand, have ready at hand</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a>, <i>taken in hand, undertaken</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>προχειρίζομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> attic <el>-χειριοῦμαι</el>: — <i>to take into one's hand, prepare for oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to choose, elect</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to determine</i> to do, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}